>You wanna screw Microsoft? Write to Aldus/Adobe and tell them that
>you want a word processor and spreadsheet with file compatibility
>across both Mac and PC platforms. Write Borland and ask for the same.
>Do the same with Novell/Wordperfect. If that doesn't loosen MS's
